00:07:51.350 --> 00:07:52.670
PROFESSOR: OK, you can
tailor the teaching

00:07:52.670 --> 00:07:53.740
style to the student.

00:07:53.740 --> 00:07:56.460
If, for example, the
student is--

00:07:56.460 --> 00:07:58.790
for example, suppose you're
teaching math to somebody

00:07:58.790 --> 00:08:00.280
who's an architect.

00:08:00.280 --> 00:08:02.670
Well, you can use lots of
